      "upsert": [
        {
          "title": "THE HERO!! ～怒れる拳に火をつけろ～",
          "ja": "ONE PUNCH！\n(Three！ Two！ One！ Kill shot！)\n参上！　必勝！　至上最強！！\nなんだってんだ？　フラストレーション　俺は止まらない\n\nONE PUNCH！　完了！　連戦連勝！\n俺は喝！！　常に勝つ！！　圧勝！！\n\nPower！ Get power！　ギリギリ限界まで\n\nHERO　俺を讃える声や　喝采なんて　欲しくはないさ\nHERO　だから　人知れず　悪と闘う\n(Nobody knows who he is.)\n天(そら)覆い　押し寄せる敵　俺は背を向けはしない\nHERO　ならば　揺るぎなき覚悟したため　繰り出せ鉄拳\n\n(Three！ Two！ One！ Fight back！)\n参上！ Go on！　正々堂々！！\nどうなってんだ？　なにも感じねぇ　もはや敵居ねー！\n\nJUSTICE！　執行！　問答無用！\n俺が断つ！！　悪を断つ！！　合掌！！\n\nPower！ Get power！　アドレナリン溢れ出すぜ！\nPower！ Get power！　鍛えた技をぶちかませ！\n\nHERO　どんなに　強い奴も　ちっぽけなガキだったんだ\nHERO　弱き　己乗り越え　強くなる\n(Nobody knows who he is.)\n神宿る　拳掲げて　俺は突き進むだけさ\nHERO　いつか　敗北に汚泥なめるまで　闘うHERO\n\n俺は諦めない　その胸に未来(あす)を描き\n目覚め行く　世界へ今　舞い上がれ　強く高く\nどんな時でも　なにがあっても\n\nHERO　俺を讃える声や　喝采なんて　欲しくはないさ\nHERO　だから　人知れず　悪と闘う\n(Nobody knows who he is.)\n神宿る　拳掲げて　俺は突き進むだけさ\nHERO　いつか　敗北に汚泥なめるまで　闘うHERO\n孤独なHERO",
          "en": "ONE PUNCH!\n(Three! Two! One! Kill shot!)\nHere I come! Certain victory! The absolute strongest!!\nWhat is this? Frustration—I will not stop.\n\nONE PUNCH! Complete! Battle after battle, victory after victory!\nI roar!! I always win!! Total victory!!\n\nPower! Get power! Right up to the very limit.\n\nHERO—I do not want voices praising me or applause.\nHERO—so I fight evil without anyone knowing.\n(Nobody knows who he is.)\nAs enemies surge in and cover the sky, I will not turn my back.\nHERO—then, with unwavering resolve prepared, unleash the iron fist.\n\n(Three! Two! One! Fight back!)\nHere I come! Go on! Fair and square!!\nWhat is going on? I do not feel anything anymore—there are no enemies left!\n\nJUSTICE! Execute! No questions asked!\nI cut down evil!! I sever evil!! Hands together in prayer!!\n\nPower! Get power! Adrenaline is overflowing!\nPower! Get power! Unleash the techniques you have trained!\n\nHERO—even the strongest guy was once just a tiny kid.\nHERO—overcoming the weak self, one becomes strong.\n(Nobody knows who he is.)\nWith a god dwelling in my raised fist, I simply keep charging ahead.\nHERO—until someday I taste defeat in the mud, I will fight, HERO.\n\nI will not give up; I draw the future in my heart.\nInto the awakening world now—rise up, strong and high.\nAt any time, no matter what happens.\n\nHERO—I do not want voices praising me or applause.\nHERO—so I fight evil without anyone knowing.\n(Nobody knows who he is.)\nWith a god dwelling in my raised fist, I simply keep charging ahead.\nHERO—until someday I taste defeat in the mud, I will fight, HERO.\nA lonely HERO.",
          "tags": [
            "song-lyrics",
            "opm-song-the_hero"
          ],
